creator: Lily Dougall
description:
LibriVox recording of A Dozen Ways of Love by Lily Dougall.
Read in English by Adrienne Koh; MaryAnn; Andrei Borissenko; Lynne Thompson; FineOrangePekoe; Mike Pelton; Natalie Paula; JamesMcAndrew
This is a collection of (each in their own way) romantic short stories by Lily Dougall. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
